name: We R Memory Keepers Photo Sleeves, 12" x 12" Post Bound Albums

reviews.name: We R Memory Keepers Photo Sleeves, 12" x 12" Post Bound Albums
reviews.reviewText: I love these things. They are the best product out there for 4x6 photos. I don't use them so much for scrapbooking, for me they are photo albums. I have a lot of photos and albums where you can only put 3 or 4 on a page just take up way too much space. These sleeves give me the most photo storage for the money. I use them with the We R Memory Keepers Albums, but you could use them with any 12 x 12 album. Have been buying them exclusively for a couple of years and am really happy. Wal-Mart has the best price on them, too! Everywhere else the price is a $1 or more higher.
reviews.title: Perfect for photo albums

reviews.name: We R Memory Keepers Photo Sleeves, 12" x 12" Post Bound Albums
reviews.reviewText: These protectors are what I would call a medium heavy weight quality (comparable to CTMH) . I was surprised they were this heavy for the small price that they were. Each pocket is top load (not mentioned in description). So far I really like them!
reviews.title: Really nice for the price
